    "This is largely due to the scarcity of substantial data in these languages that is required for training these models.",
    "Here, human lexicographers may have an advantage, particularly in their ability to generalize and extrapolate from limited datasets.",
    "Consequently, lexicography remains vital for bridging linguistic divides and preserving the linguistic diversity of these smaller language communities.",
